 show that areas of native regeneration and exotic tree plantations can provide complementary conservation services, we also provide clear empirical evidence demonstrating the irreplaceable value of primary forests.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Barlow, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gardner, T. A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Araujo, I. S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "\u00c1vila-Pires, T. C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bonaldo, A. B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Costa, J. E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Esposito, M. C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ferreira, L. V.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hawes, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hernandez, M. I. M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hoogmoed, M. S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Leite, R. N.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lo-Man-Hung, N. F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Malcolm, J. R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Martins, M. B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mestre, L. A. M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Miranda-Santos, R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nunes-Gutjahr, A. L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Overal, W. L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Parry, L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Peters, S. L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ribeiro-Junior, M. A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Da Silva, M. N. F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Da Silva Motta, C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Peres, C. A.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c22089d8cd09b52d87aae6b1e11df59c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/9ebd8e6461b998c8949b48fd21b7cda1631e651cf528dda13cdb50fb189fc84b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/X6Y6FCYW", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifie